                    2626,
                    2164,
                    2729
                ],
                "angle": 0,
                "content": "3 Basic Law: The Knesset, SH 5718 No. 244, p. 69, as amended, https://perma.cc/XLD6-WQWQ (unofficial English translation)."
            },
